# .trivyignore — CVEs intentionally ignored with justification
#
# Format: CVE-ID
# Each entry must have a justification comment above it.

# CVE-2023-45853 (zlib): Only exploitable via a crafted file processed by minigzip/minizip.
# Our app never processes zlib-compressed files directly — Flask uses zlib only for
# HTTP transfer encoding which is not exposed to untrusted input in this deployment.
# CVE-2023-45853

# CVE-2024-2236 (libgcrypt): Timing side-channel in RSA decryption.
# Our app does not perform RSA decryption. libgcrypt is a transitive dependency
# of system packages and is not directly used by application code.
# CVE-2024-2236
